Take Shelter;;81;;92;;R;;Curtis LaForche (Michael Shannon) lives in a small Ohio town with his loving wife (Jessica Chastain) and hearing-impaired daughter (Tova Stewart). Though money is tight, he and his family are very happy. But then, Curtis begins having terrifying dreams about an apocalypse that threatens them all. Rather than confiding in Samantha, he begins building a storm shelter in the backyard, and his strange behavior causes tension in their marriage and the surrounding community.;;Drama,Mystery & thriller;;Jeff Nichols;;2011;;Michael Shannon,Jessica Chastain,Shea Whigham,Katy Mixon,Ray McKinnon,LisaGay Hamilton,Robert Longstreet,Kathy Baker,Tova Stewart;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/take_shelter